{"type": "article", "id": 6332, "title": "无线音响 Sugr Cube", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-16T07:40:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234344LNORSd54Hpq2MZha.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tSugr Cube 是一款支持手势控制的无线音响，它有着特别的木制外壳，颇具几分文艺气质。它内置了豆瓣电台，Pandora 以及 BBC 等音乐服务，可在 Wi-Fi 环境下使用。Sugr Cube 没有任何按钮，采用了自然的体感交互方式，轻触操作暂停与播放功能，左右摇晃可以换曲，长触还可以分享歌曲，续航时间为 7 小时。目前，Sugr Cube 正在 kickstarter 上众筹，起售价 139 美元（约合人民币 867 元），<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1350952796/sugr-cube-touch-to-stream-and-share-music#\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>，预计今年 7 月出货。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODY1MDgwNzI4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/003/117/432/304535954896524bdeb1eae76b2c8c19_large.gif?1420700188\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/003/117/441/f14c6d00ccf1be6cd83b2a0ba2eb5eab_large.gif?1420700493\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/003/117/445/0330629c0b0851be400205bbedde5649_large.gif?1420700571\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}